# Frontend

The ExactPay frontend provides a simple, mobile-first experience designed for global migrants.

## Planned User Flow

1. User Sign In
2. Identity Verification
3. Transfer Amount Entry
4. Exact Recipient Amount Confirmation
5. Payment Authorization
6. Transaction Status
7. Portable Financial Profile

## Planned Features

- Mobile-first responsive interface
- Secure authentication
- Reusable digital identity
- Financial certainty dashboard
- Offline-first transaction preparation
- Payment history
- Financial profile

The frontend will be implemented as the user interface for the ExactPay platform.
